{
  "text": "To determine the PET/CT parameters, SUV max , MTV and TLG were obtained for the primary tumor based on the previously described method [CITATION_1] . In brief, SUV max represents the highest activity of a single pixel within the tumor, and MTV measures the volume of the metabolically active tumor. TLG, which is the multiplication of MTV and SUV mean , signifies the overall tumor burden [CITATION_2] .",
